node.text: Y'all know I wasn't playing when I said we've been at this collection for over a YEAR! We're throwing that sh$t back and letting you peek into my creative process with my legit favorites everrrr @ilmakiage 💚 We spent a looonnggg assss time not gonna lie swatching dozens of shades, perfecting these pigments, figuring out the formulas and designing a whole bunch of themes together 🔥 They worked so damn hard to bring every piece of my vision to life so we could give y’all the most lit collection ever and you KNOW my debut into the makeup world had to be straight FIRE! Who’s ready ??? 8/27 !!!! 💚🖤
